<div class="flex flex-col">
    <span class="xl:text-headline2 md:text-15 md:leading-[48px] text-headline3 text-brand">FAQ</span>
</div>

<div>
    <ul class="list-unstyled cursor-pointer">
        <li class="flex flex-col gap-L border-b border-brNeutral p-L items-center hover:bg-[#EFEEEB]" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
           <div class="flex justify-between w-full">
             <span class="text-H4 text-headLines">Where is Unilake based?</span>
               <span class="text-brand flex items-center cursor-pointer" tabindex="1">
                   <svg class="accordion-icon" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                       <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M12 4.25C12.4142 4.25 12.75 4.58579 12.75 5V11.25H19C19.4142 11.25 19.75 11.5858 19.75 12C19.75 12.4142 19.4142 12.75 19 12.75H12.75V19C12.75 19.4142 12.4142 19.75 12 19.75C11.5858 19.75 11.25 19.4142 11.25 19V12.75H5C4.58579 12.75 4.25 12.4142 4.25 12C4.25 11.5858 4.58579 11.25 5 11.25H11.25V5C11.25 4.58579 11.5858 4.25 12 4.25Z" fill="#FF6849"/>
                   </svg>
               </span>
           </div>
           <p class="w-full hidden text-bodyText text-Regular">
               Unilake is a Dutch company based in The Netherlands, contributors come from over the world
           </p>
        </li>
    </ul>
    <ul class="list-unstyled cursor-pointer">
        <li class="flex flex-col gap-L border-b border-brNeutral p-L items-center hover:bg-[#EFEEEB]" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
           <div class="flex justify-between w-full">
             <span class="text-H4 text-headLines">What do I need to run Unilake?</span>
               <span class="text-brand flex items-center cursor-pointer" tabindex="1">
                   <svg class="accordion-icon" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                       <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M12 4.25C12.4142 4.25 12.75 4.58579 12.75 5V11.25H19C19.4142 11.25 19.75 11.5858 19.75 12C19.75 12.4142 19.4142 12.75 19 12.75H12.75V19C12.75 19.4142 12.4142 19.75 12 19.75C11.5858 19.75 11.25 19.4142 11.25 19V12.75H5C4.58579 12.75 4.25 12.4142 4.25 12C4.25 11.5858 4.58579 11.25 5 11.25H11.25V5C11.25 4.58579 11.5858 4.25 12 4.25Z" fill="#FF6849"/>
                   </svg>
               </span>
           </div>
           <p class="w-full hidden text-bodyText text-Regular">
               At a minimum you need a Kubernetes cluster and a storage solution (S3, Azure Storage, GCP Storage, HDFS). This can be cloud based or self-hosted.
           </p>
        </li>
    </ul>
    <ul class="list-unstyled cursor-pointer">
        <li class="flex flex-col gap-L border-b border-brNeutral p-L items-center hover:bg-[#EFEEEB]" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
           <div class="flex justify-between w-full">
             <span class="text-H4 text-headLines">What is the current state of development?</span>
               <span class="text-brand flex items-center cursor-pointer" tabindex="1">
                   <svg class="accordion-icon" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                       <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M12 4.25C12.4142 4.25 12.75 4.58579 12.75 5V11.25H19C19.4142 11.25 19.75 11.5858 19.75 12C19.75 12.4142 19.4142 12.75 19 12.75H12.75V19C12.75 19.4142 12.4142 19.75 12 19.75C11.5858 19.75 11.25 19.4142 11.25 19V12.75H5C4.58579 12.75 4.25 12.4142 4.25 12C4.25 11.5858 4.58579 11.25 5 11.25H11.25V5C11.25 4.58579 11.5858 4.25 12 4.25Z" fill="#FF6849"/>
                   </svg>
               </span>
           </div>
           <p class="w-full hidden text-bodyText text-Regular">
               Unilake is currently in active development. We are working on features and refining the platform in order to launch our Alpha version.
           </p>
        </li>
    </ul>
    <ul class="list-unstyled cursor-pointer">
        <li class="flex flex-col gap-L border-b border-brNeutral p-L items-center hover:bg-[#EFEEEB]" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
           <div class="flex justify-between w-full">
             <span class="text-H4 text-headLines">I found a bug, or I am having issues, what now?</span>
               <span class="text-brand flex items-center cursor-pointer" tabindex="1">
                   <svg class="accordion-icon" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                       <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M12 4.25C12.4142 4.25 12.75 4.58579 12.75 5V11.25H19C19.4142 11.25 19.75 11.5858 19.75 12C19.75 12.4142 19.4142 12.75 19 12.75H12.75V19C12.75 19.4142 12.4142 19.75 12 19.75C11.5858 19.75 11.25 19.4142 11.25 19V12.75H5C4.58579 12.75 4.25 12.4142 4.25 12C4.25 11.5858 4.58579 11.25 5 11.25H11.25V5C11.25 4.58579 11.5858 4.25 12 4.25Z" fill="#FF6849"/>
                   </svg>
               </span>
           </div>
           <p class="w-full hidden text-bodyText text-Regular">
               Best is to reach out to us via our zulip chat: <a href="https://chat.unilake.com">chat.unilake.com</a>
           </p>
        </li>
    </ul>
</div>

<script>
    function toggleFAQ(accordion) {
        var content = accordion.children[1];
        if (content.style.display === "none" || content.style.display === "") {
            content.style.display = "block";
            accordion.querySelector('.accordion-icon').classList.add('rotate-45');
        } else {
            content.style.display = "none";
            accordion.querySelector('.accordion-icon').classList.remove('rotate-45');
        }
    }
</script>
